<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>基础属性</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">▼基础魔抗由32.1降低到28。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200923/7b7511b399ce42839c0ab92cb61e3793.png" max-width="600" /></p>
