<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>基础属性</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">▼基础护甲由32降低到29</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200923/6f30c0ab3e784a459ddf3d081986cb11.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>沙漠玫瑰 莎弥拉</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>基础属性</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">▼基础生命值由600降低到530。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>R-炼狱扳机</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">▼总基础伤害由100/200/300降低到0/100/200。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">▼总AD加成由6.0降低到5.0。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200923/40256836b7244439aeefd696d9e27767.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>无畏战车 厄加特</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>被动-回响烈焰</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>▲</strong>对野怪的伤害由60-360提升到100-360。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>W-净除</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>▲</strong>新：命中野怪时，最少造成50点伤害。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>云顶改动</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>法师</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">6英雄：法术强度提升由120回调到110。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>夜幽</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">6英雄：法术强度提升由50/75%降低到40/70%。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>黛安娜</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">法球的数量由3/4/6/10提升到4/5/6/10。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>丽桑卓</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">技能主要伤害由300/400/600/900提升到350/450/600/900。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">技能次要伤害由150/200/300/450提升到175/225/300/450。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>安妮</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">技能伤害由200/300/450提升到250/350/450。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">技能护盾由400/600/900提升到500/700/900。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>厄斐琉斯</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">技能持续时间由6/7/8/11秒提升到7/8/9/11秒。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>赫卡里姆</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">技能治疗量由250/350/500提升到250/400/600。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>新皮肤</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">至臻瑟提原画曝光。</p>
